---

<PageLayout
  title="Sobre mí"
  description="Conoce más sobre Jhoselin Quispe Luque, estudiante de Ingeniería Industrial en la Universidad Continental - Cusco, enfocada en mejora de procesos y análisis de datos."
>
  <!-- Hero Section - with background image like naisser.com -->
  <section class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full">
      <img
        src="/images/profile/fondo hero.jpg"
        alt=""
        class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <!-- Dark overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 py-16 text-center sm:py-20">
      <!-- Profile Image - Circular -->
      <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <div class="relative mx-auto h-32 w-32 sm:h-40 sm:w-40 md:h-48 md:w-48 lg:h-56 lg:w-56">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-4 border-white/80 shadow-2xl"></div>
          <img
            src="/images/profile/foto 1.jpeg"
            alt="Jhoselin Quispe Luque"
            class="h-full w-full rounded-full object-cover object-top"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Name -->
      <h1
        class="mb-3 px-4 text-xl font-bold text-white sm:mb-4 sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl"
      >
        <span class="text-white/95">Estudiante Ing. </span>
        <span class="text-primary">JHOSELIN QUISPE LUQUE</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Description -->
      <p
        class="mx-auto mb-6 max-w-xl px-6 text-xs leading-relaxed text-white/85 sm:mb-8 sm:px-4 sm:text-sm md:text-base lg:max-w-2xl"
      >
        Soy estudiante de Ingeniería Industrial en la Universidad Continental - Cusco, actualmente
        en el 5to semestre. Me apasiona el análisis de procesos, la mejora continua y el uso de la
        tecnología para optimizar la toma de decisiones. En esta web quiero compartir mis proyectos
        y experiencias académicas contigo.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Button -->
      <a
        href="#profile"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-primary/90 sm:px-8 sm:py-3 sm:text-base"
      >
        Ver más
        <svg
          class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Profile Section - naisser.com style (two columns) -->
  <section id="profile" class="section bg-white dark:bg-background">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
          <!-- Image side -->
          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="/images/profile/foto 2.jpeg"
              alt="Jhoselin Quispe Luque"
              class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm rounded-xl object-cover shadow-lg sm:max-w-md lg:mx-0"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Text content -->
          <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
            <h2
              class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl"
            >
              JHOSELIN QUISPE LUQUE
            </h2>

            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground sm:text-base">
              Estudiante de Ingeniería Industrial · 5to Semestre
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
              <p
                class="text-xs italic leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-sm md:text-base"
              >
                Estudio Ingeniería Industrial en la Universidad Continental - Cusco. Me caracterizo
                por un enfoque reflexivo y analítico, buscando siempre comprender el "por qué"
                detrás de cada problema antes de plantear soluciones.
              </p>

              <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-sm md:text-base">
                Me apasiona la mejora de procesos, el análisis de datos y la aplicación de
                tecnologías emergentes como la Inteligencia Artificial en contextos industriales.
                Considero el aprendizaje constante como un pilar fundamental de mi desarrollo.
              </p>

              <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-sm md:text-base">
                He participado en diversos proyectos académicos y eventos relacionados con
                metodologías de calidad, gestión de operaciones y optimización. Mi objetivo es
                aplicar herramientas de ingeniería para resolver problemas reales en organizaciones.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Buttons -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2 sm:gap-3 sm:pt-4">
              <a
                href="/projects"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-white transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-primary/90 sm:px-6 sm:py-2.5 sm:text-sm"
                >Ver Proyectos</a
              >
              <a
                href="/events"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-white transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-primary/90 sm:px-6 sm:py-2.5 sm:text-sm"
                >Ver Eventos</a
              >
              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-white transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-primary/90 sm:px-6 sm:py-2.5 sm:text-sm"
                >Contactar</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services/Areas Section - naisser.com style cards -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary/30">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {
          areasExpertise.map((area) => (
            <article class="service-card">
              <div class="service-card-icon">
                <svg
                  class="h-full w-full"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                >
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={area.icono} />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="service-card-title">{area.titulo}</h3>
              <p class="service-card-description">{area.descripcion}</p>
            </article>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education Section -->
  <section class="section bg-background">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="mb-8 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="text-foreground">Formación </span>
            <span class="text-primary">Académica</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
          {
            formacionAcademica.map((item) => (
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
                  <span class="badge-primary text-xs">{item.periodo}</span>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-green-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-green-700 dark:bg-green-900/30 dark:text-green-400">
                    {item.estado}
                  </span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-bold text-foreground">{item.titulo}</h3>
                <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary">{item.institucion}</p>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">{item.descripcion}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills Section -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary/30">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        <div class="mb-8 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="text-foreground">Mis </span>
            <span class="text-primary">Habilidades</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Technical Skills -->
          <div class="card-professional">
            <h3 class="mb-5 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold text-foreground">
              <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
                <svg
                  class="h-5 w-5 text-primary"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              Habilidades Técnicas
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-5">
              {
                habilidadesTecnicas.map((skill) => (
                  <div>
                    <div class="mb-2 flex justify-between">
                      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">{skill.nombre}</span>
                      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">{skill.porcentaje}%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="skill-bar">
                      <div class="skill-bar-fill" style={`width: ${skill.porcentaje}%`} />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                ))
              }
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Soft Skills -->
          <div class="card-professional">
            <h3 class="mb-5 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold text-foreground">
              <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
                <svg
                  class="h-5 w-5 text-primary"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              Habilidades Blandas
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-5">
              {
                habilidadesBlandas.map((skill) => (
                  <div>
                    <div class="mb-2 flex justify-between">
                      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">{skill.nombre}</span>
                      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">{skill.porcentaje}%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="skill-bar">
                      <div class="skill-bar-fill" style={`width: ${skill.porcentaje}%`} />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                ))
              }
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section tech-pattern-bg text-white">
    <div class="hero-lines"></div>
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl">
          <span class="text-white">¿Quieres saber más sobre </span>
          <span class="text-primary">mis proyectos?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mb-6 max-w-xl text-sm text-white/80 sm:text-base">
          Explora mis trabajos académicos y proyectos de mejora continua desarrollados durante mi
          formación.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">
            Ver Proyectos
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 sm:px-6 sm:py-2.5"
          >
            Contactar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
